the heart of man.

18:19.399 --> 18:21.968
That's Kabu, my dear.

18:21.968 --> 18:23.236
- [Female] Lucian.

18:23.236 --> 18:24.070
- Hmm?

18:27.607 --> 18:31.778
Muse, I thought you were
staying with your mother.

18:35.315 --> 18:37.150
- It's Tuesday, Daddy.

18:41.588 --> 18:42.755
- Well then...

18:44.224 --> 18:46.125
Well sit Muse, join us.

18:53.533 --> 18:55.968
Would you like some coffee?

18:55.968 --> 18:58.070
- I don't know, I
should get to school.

18:58.070 --> 18:59.406
- Nonsense, sit.

19:16.623 --> 19:20.893
Cali, this is Ashley,
she's my graduate student.

19:20.893 --> 19:21.894
- Hey, sure.

19:23.296 --> 19:24.831
I gotta get to class.

19:24.831 --> 19:25.665
- Sit!

19:30.102 --> 19:30.937
- Okay.

19:34.006 --> 19:37.677
- Ashley, this is my
daughter Cali, my muse.

19:46.553 --> 19:50.723
Ashley is quite the star in
our humble little bailiwick.

19:51.958 --> 19:54.894
She's doing her thesis
on the age of reason,

19:54.894 --> 19:56.829
very provocative stuff.

20:02.435 --> 20:04.637
- I'm doing this third
way feminist view of it.

20:04.637 --> 20:07.907
You know, breaking
down the relationship

20:07.907 --> 20:09.709
between the mostly
male existentialist--

20:09.709 --> 20:11.711
- I'm sorry but
this is bullshit.

20:11.711 --> 20:12.912
- [Father] Cali.

20:12.912 --> 20:15.415
- Not your thesis,
sorry, it sounds very,

20:15.415 --> 20:18.585
you know, interesting,
or whatever, I gotta go.

20:18.585 --> 20:21.921
- Cali, I'm afraid
you're being a child.

20:28.094 --> 20:31.764
- Don't feel bad, I
know he's very charming.

20:38.438 --> 20:41.207
(low dark music)

20:50.817 --> 20:53.386
(birds cawing)

21:03.062 --> 21:06.566
- You buy it, or you
stop playing with it.

22:00.787 --> 22:04.957
- You wouldn't like it, it's
all full of words and stuff.

22:06.125 --> 22:07.627
- Made of Athens
air we part, give,

22:07.627 --> 22:09.796
oh, give me back my heart.

