truant like you quote Byron,

22:40.059 --> 22:41.461
what's your deal?

22:42.862 --> 22:46.298
- Like you said,
I'm a smart one.

22:46.298 --> 22:47.900
- Yeah, I can tell.

22:49.669 --> 22:50.837
You know, I ain't your daddy,

22:50.837 --> 22:54.541
but aren't you supposed
to be in school?

22:54.541 --> 22:55.842
- I'll go when they
can teach me something

22:55.842 --> 22:57.544
they haven't learned
in their ignominious

22:57.544 --> 22:59.679
little community
college educations.

22:59.679 --> 23:01.881
(laughing)

23:06.152 --> 23:08.821
- Jesus Christ, how old are you?

23:11.958 --> 23:12.792
- 18.

23:15.928 --> 23:18.164
- Uh huh, what's your name?

23:20.767 --> 23:23.035
- What do you care?

23:23.035 --> 23:24.604
- What's your name?

23:29.909 --> 23:34.080
- Cali, Calliope really, but
only my dad calls me that.

23:37.283 --> 23:41.220
- It's kind of a faggy
name, is your daddy a fag.

23:41.220 --> 23:44.290
- (laughing) Hardly.

23:45.725 --> 23:47.460
- Calliope, the muse.

23:52.398 --> 23:55.802
- Yeah, he's the only one
who calls me that too.

23:55.802 --> 23:57.704
- Ah, I get it, issues.

24:02.975 --> 24:03.810
Here.

24:19.659 --> 24:22.495
Take it, it will
make daddy happy.

24:24.831 --> 24:27.266
- I don't have issues.

24:27.266 --> 24:29.802
