- I'm sorry, I thought we
were talking about issues.

24:48.855 --> 24:51.758
- You don't back off, do you?

24:51.758 --> 24:52.592
- Nope.

24:59.131 --> 25:01.968
- I'm Billy, yeah,
I killed people.

25:11.010 --> 25:11.944
- How many?

25:19.652 --> 25:21.153
- I like you Cali.

25:25.725 --> 25:29.896
- I don't believe you, I don't
think you killed anybody.

26:01.360 --> 26:05.531
- Stop by the next time you
want to escape the ignominy.

26:20.179 --> 26:21.013
See ya.

