30:38.370 --> 30:41.807
- I think maybe, this
isn't a great idea.

30:46.012 --> 30:48.747
I'm old enough to
be your father.

30:50.816 --> 30:52.418
- But you're not...

30:55.421 --> 30:56.255
My father.

31:03.362 --> 31:04.863
- Hey, look at me.

31:07.766 --> 31:08.767
You're sure?

31:09.969 --> 31:10.802
- Yeah.

31:19.111 --> 31:20.446
