31:39.498 --> 31:43.669
- So, I told them that the play
was about a rabid populous.

31:45.137 --> 31:49.308
And they looked at me with
these longing, willful,

31:49.308 --> 31:52.844
naive stares that only a
college freshman could have,

31:52.844 --> 31:55.747
hoping that I was not
writing another tirade

31:55.747 --> 31:58.184
