32:34.286 --> 32:35.687
- Where were you?

32:41.193 --> 32:45.031
You are not going to
drink out of that carton.

32:48.967 --> 32:52.304
Still haven't
answered my question.

32:52.304 --> 32:54.006
- I was at dads.

32:54.006 --> 32:56.175
- Uh huh, and how was dad?

33:12.058 --> 33:14.560
- What is that, what the fuck.

33:19.998 --> 33:22.268
(knocking)

33:25.571 --> 33:28.574
Holy shit, uh Jesus
Christ, come in.

33:34.280 --> 33:35.681
