with me, did I?

36:52.210 --> 36:53.879
- No, of course not.

36:59.385 --> 37:01.987
- I just found this at my house.

37:06.958 --> 37:09.295
And that, is that a seizure.

37:15.267 --> 37:19.438
I was hoping, I thought maybe
you could tell me where he is.

37:24.276 --> 37:25.677
- Absolutely not.

37:27.446 --> 37:30.081
No way in hell,
Jesus Christ Cali,

37:30.081 --> 37:32.984
you were like my
one success story.

37:34.085 --> 37:35.787
Do you remember what you were

37:35.787 --> 37:37.289
like when you got out of there?

37:37.289 --> 37:41.026
I do, 80 pounds, at most,
somebody would slam a door,

37:41.026 --> 37:42.594
you'd nearly jump
