37:42.594 --> 37:44.763
You remember that, do you?

37:45.964 --> 37:46.898
Look at me.

37:54.440 --> 37:55.707
Calliope, stop!

38:01.246 --> 38:02.080
Why?

38:03.515 --> 38:07.386
- I don't want to talk to
him Selena, or see him.

38:11.790 --> 38:14.460
I just need to know where he is.

38:16.662 --> 38:18.497
- I don't believe you.

38:19.931 --> 38:23.669
