who you think I am.

56:17.775 --> 56:20.778
- Please, don't do
this, I love you.

56:26.484 --> 56:27.918
- I love you too.

56:33.190 --> 56:35.593
- So, what about the drawing?

56:37.027 --> 56:37.928
- It doesn't matter.

56:37.928 --> 56:38.863
- Calliope!

56:38.863 --> 56:41.365
- Look, I have to go somewhere,

56:47.772 --> 56:49.440
to talk to somebody.

56:50.575 --> 56:51.408
- Him?

56:54.779 --> 56:57.615
- I don't know,
maybe, I hope not.

57:00.885 --> 57:02.720
- I wanna go with you.

57:07.792 --> 57:09.393
- I'm sorry.

57:09.393 --> 57:11.562
- I don't understand this.

57:12.897 --> 57:14.131
Do you still...

57:18.669 --> 57:20.505
Do you still want him?

57:40.558 --> 57:44.194
- I want the best environment
for her too, I do.

57:44.194 --> 57:47.665
What am I doing, how
do you know that?

57:47.665 --> 57:50.234
That's what I used to do Kay,
I'm trying to be a father now,

57:50.234 --> 57:53.137
I'm trying to be a
member of a family,

57:53.137 --> 57:54.972
and that's what you said--

57:54.972 --> 57:56.541
- Bill, you better get
your ass in here before--

57:56.541 --> 57:57.875
- That's all you talk about now.

57:57.875 --> 58:00.210
I want to, I'd learned that.

58:02.547 --> 58:05.382
No, that's what this is, I
know that, I know the legal.

58:05.382 --> 58:08.886
God damn it Kay, she's
my fucking kid too.

58:13.858 --> 58:18.028
Yeah, well, I'm not the one
who's being a cunt about it!

58:19.429 --> 58:23.167
- Gotta listen to him shout
like that all the time?

58:26.170 --> 58:30.340
- Don't fucking bogart,
okay, this shit ain't cheap!

58:36.747 --> 58:37.582
- Billy?

58:39.149 --> 58:41.652
- You having a flashback Bill?

58:57.201 --> 58:58.035
- Billy.

59:00.971 --> 59:02.406
- Don't!

59:02.406 --> 59:05.075
(light gasping)

59:26.496 --> 59:28.332
(laughing)

59:28.332 --> 59:29.166
- Get out!

59:30.500 --> 59:33.671
(exciting rock music)

01:00:29.760 --> 01:00:32.362
