01:00:37.134 --> 01:00:38.903
- [Billy] Look at me.

01:00:54.685 --> 01:00:56.086
Cali, look at me.

01:01:04.862 --> 01:01:07.197
- [Roy] What about your mom?

01:01:12.302 --> 01:01:17.141
I got room, you know, if
you need a place, anything,

01:01:17.141 --> 01:01:19.877
you know, no
strings, or nothing.

01:01:21.278 --> 01:01:23.113
- I don't know, maybe.

01:01:26.416 --> 01:01:29.419
- [Roy] I'd really
like to draw you.

01:01:31.989 --> 01:01:35.059
(laughing)

01:01:35.059 --> 01:01:36.460
What, I can draw.

01:02:53.403 --> 01:02:54.238
- Billy?

01:03:12.256 --> 01:03:14.324
- I'm sorry I scared you.

01:03:16.160 --> 01:03:18.395
- It's okay, what happened?

01:03:23.100 --> 01:03:25.202
What did she say to you?

01:03:25.202 --> 01:03:26.871
- Don't leave, okay?

01:03:29.339 --> 01:03:30.174
- What?

01:03:34.778 --> 01:03:37.514
- You can kill me
if you want to,

01:03:39.183 --> 01:03:43.353
slit my throat in my sleep or
something, just don't leave.

01:03:46.490 --> 01:03:49.894
- I'm not going to
kill you Billy, Jesus.

01:03:56.600 --> 01:04:00.670
And I'm not going anywhere,
you're stuck with me.

01:04:06.543 --> 01:04:10.480
- Lovers and mad men have
such seething brains.

01:04:18.255 --> 01:04:21.591
- Such shaping fantasies
that apprehend,

01:04:22.993 --> 01:04:26.430
more than quarries,
it never comprehends.

01:04:32.736 --> 01:04:35.906
- I live in this neighborhood,
